# Dungeon Forge - Environment Variables
# Copiar a .env.local y completar con valores reales (NUNCA hacer commit de .env)
# ADVERTENCIA: Nunca hacer commit de archivos .env o google-services.json con claves reales

# ============================================================================
# Firebase Configuration (obtener de Firebase Console > Project Settings)
# ============================================================================
VITE_FIREBASE_API_KEY=AIzaSy... [generate new Android API key in Google Cloud Console]
VITE_FIREBASE_AUTH_DOMAIN=dungeon-forge-prod.firebaseapp.com
VITE_FIREBASE_PROJECT_ID=dungeon-forge-prod
VITE_FIREBASE_STORAGE_BUCKET=dungeon-forge-prod.firebasestorage.app
VITE_FIREBASE_MESSAGING_SENDER_ID=955477498217
VITE_FIREBASE_APP_ID=1:955477498217:web:...
VITE_FIREBASE_DATABASE_URL=https://dungeon-forge-prod-default-rtdb.firebaseio.com

# ============================================================================
# Google OAuth API Key for Android
# ============================================================================
# IMPORTANTE: Create this key in Google Cloud Console with:
# - Type: API key
# - Application restrictions: Android apps
# - Package name: com.tupaquete.dndcompanion
# - SHA-1 certificate fingerprint: (get from Android build)
VITE_GOOGLE_API_KEY=AIzaSy... [new restricted Android API key]
